question 'What is one major weakness of AI compared to human intelligence?'

right 'AI lacks creativity and true understanding, relying only on patterns and probability.'
wrong 'AI makes no mistakes because it processes data with perfect accuracy.'
wrong 'AI can reason and think critically just like humans.'
wrong 'AI always provides unbiased responses since it was programmed by humans.'

